<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 07 at 9:44PM EST  by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>...PATCHY FREEZING DRIZZLE THIS EVENING...
Patchy freezing drizzle could occur in some parts of the region
through this evening in the southwest Adirondacks, Mohawk Valley,
Schoharie Valley, Saratoga Region and the Capital District. Where
freezing drizzle does occur, some icy spots may develop on
untreated roads and walking surfaces. Use caution if out and about
the rest of the evening.</description>
